  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div xml:id="KT1-kilavi">
          <p type="edition">tōḻi kaiyuṟai maṟuttatu.</p>
          <p type="translation" xml:lang="en">The confidante refusing [the acceptance of his] present.</p>
        </div>
        <div xml:id="KT1">
            <lg type="edition"><l>ceṅkaḷam paṭakkoṉ ṟavuṇart tēytta</l>
<l>ceṅkō lampiṟ ceṅkōṭ ṭiyāṉaik</l>
<l>kaḻaṟoṭic cēey kuṉṟaṅ</l>
<l>kurutip pūviṉ kulaikkān taṭṭē.</l>
            </lg>
            <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>           Red the ground from killing, the demons reduced</l>
<l rend="indent">by red-stemmed arrows, red-tusked elephants,</l>
<l>anklets,
    <choice>
        <seg>bracelets</seg>
        <seg>becoming loose –</seg>
    </choice>
</l>
<l rend="indent">–the red one's hill</l>
<l rend="indent4">full of Malabar lilies, a bunch of blood-flowers.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
